data.description: Enjoy sunsets overlooking the lake from your front courtyard.  Highly upgraded expanded Lily model home in active retiree community. Huge master suite w/ bay window, massive master bath w/ juzucci tub, his/hers vanities, custom his/hers walk-in closets.  Upgraded kitchen w/ pullout shelves, built-in frig, s/s appliances, island, granite countertops, double ovens, large walk-in pantry.  Family room comes complete w/ corner nook/desk. Surround sound in family room & master bedroom. Den w/ maple bookcase & built-in desk. Brazilian hardwood floors in living area & den. New carpet & paint, shutters, Laundry room w/ extra cabinets/clothes rack. Extended garage w/ built-in cabinets. Third car garage can be studio, workshop, craft room w/ air conditioning, sink,& electricity.  See it today.
